      "[Cysaegir, Wishing Well]"
    ],
    "description": [
      "Nestled beneath the peacefully spreading branches of several tanik trees is a charming, fel-gabled edifice.  Set in the elegant bay window, a lone candle burns and an inviting soft light spills forth from the opened window.  A wishing well, affixed with a polished plaque set in its center stands not far off from the building.  Trumpet-shaped purple blossoms of mournblooms snake along the lip of the wishing well and vines of creeping clematis drape down the sides.",
      "Nestled beneath the peacefully spreading branches of several tanik trees is a charming, fel-gabled edifice.  Glimpsed from the open bay window, a set of ivory brocade drapes billow on a soft breeze.  A wishing well, affixed with a polished plaque set at its center stands not far off from the building.  Trumpet-shaped purple blossoms of mournblooms snake along the lip of the wishing well and vines of creeping clematis drape down the sides."
